---
title: Saucy Beyond Meat® Cheeseburgers and Fried Onions with Sweet Potato Wedges and BBQ Sauce
description: These  Beyond Meat® burgers pack a flavourful punch thanks to cheddar cheese, savoury fried onions and a DIY BBQ fry sauce. Don't worry, there's enough sauce to dip the roasted sweet potatoes in too!
